Running the script

Install Boto3:
pip install boto3


Run the Script:
python script.py --instance-id i-123456789 --sns-topic arn:aws:sns:us-east-1:123456789012:Devops-Alerts


On IAM

IAM Permissions Required
Ensure that the AWS credentials used have the necessary permissions to perform the following actions:

ec2:RebootInstances
sns:Publish
You can set up these permissions using an IAM policy attached to the IAM user or role